26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_disp_cursnv50.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "channv50.h"
30#include "rootnv50.h"
31
32#include <core/client.h>
33
34#include <nvif/class.h>
35#include <nvif/unpack.h>
36
37int
38nv50_disp_curs_new(const struct nv50_disp_chan_func *func,
39 const struct nv50_disp_chan_mthd *mthd,
40 struct nv50_disp_root *root, int chid,
41 const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass, void *data, u32 size,
42 struct nvkm_object **pobject)
43{
44 union {
45 struct nv50_disp_cursor_v0 v0;
46 } *args = data;
47 struct nvkm_object *parent = oclass->parent;
48 struct nv50_disp *disp = root->disp;
49 int head, ret;
50
51 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create disp cursor size %d\n", size);
52 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
53 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create disp cursor vers %d head %d\n",
54 args->v0.version, args->v0.head);
55 if (args->v0.head > disp->base.head.nr)
56 return -EINVAL;
57 head = args->v0.head;
58 } else
59 return ret;
60
61 return nv50_disp_chan_new_(func, mthd, root, chid + head,
62 head, oclass, pobject);
63}
64
65const struct nv50_disp_pioc_oclass
66nv50_disp_curs_oclass = {
67 .base.oclass = NV50_DISP_CURSOR,
68 .base.minver = 0,
69 .base.maxver = 0,
70 .ctor = nv50_disp_curs_new,
71 .func = &nv50_disp_pioc_func,
72 .chid = 7,
73};
